{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"af8eda2d5c","title":"对中央关于反对右倾思想的指示稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3d454fc08a","index":0,"year":1959,"month":8,"day":7,"articleId":"af8eda2d5c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"629bb11e99","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"af8eda2d5c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央的这一指示稿指出，现在右倾思想已经成为工作中的主要危险，如果不彻底加以批判和克服，党的总路线的贯彻执行是不可能的，各项建设事业的继续跃进是不可能的，今年调整后的生产指标和基本建设计划的完成，也是不可能的。各级党组织，必须抓紧八、九两月，鼓足干劲，坚决反对右倾思想，厉行增产节约，提高质量，降低成本，全面安排和节约使用劳动力、物力和财力。反右倾，鼓干劲，现在是时候了。机不可失，时不再来。1959年8月7日，中共中央将这一指示下发给各省市自治区党委、中央各部委、国家机关和人民团体各党组、总政、团中央。"},{"id":"900e8827c5","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"af8eda2d5c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央书记处书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3ddc3745df","type":"title","text":"对中央关于反对右倾思想的指示稿的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"af8eda2d5c"},{"id":"629bb11e99","type":"paragraph","text":"退彭真叫同志照发","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"af8eda2d5c"},{"id":"900e8827c5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"af8eda2d5c"},{"id":"05e0fa433e","type":"paragraph","text":"八月七日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"af8eda2d5c"}],"page":{"id":"d5da1f42e6","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"af8eda2d5c","start":268,"end":268}}}},"__N_SSG":true}